# SIMS Backend

Smart Inventory Management System backend built with Flask and MySQL.

## Features
- 🔐 Login & Logout
- 📦 Add/Edit/Delete Inventory
- 🔍 Search, Filter, Pagination
- 📊 Charts (Chart.js)
- 📄 CSV & PDF Export
- 🧠 RESTful API
- 🕵️ Activity Log
- 🌙 Dark Mode Ready

## Tech Stack
- Flask
- MySQL
- Chart.js
- Bootstrap

